cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SI 

The paper focuses on the construction of an effective solution for spatio-temporal data to predict large-scale traffic state, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the design of features and optimization of models, which are related to artificial intelligence (AI) and information retrieval (IR) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions the fusion of interdisciplinary knowledge and experience, which falls under the scope of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
